item.title: TBT: My AE86 in Daikokufuto
item.description: This service area in Yokohama might be the most famous place on earth for car fans. The regular meetings of car of all ranges is well known. Thus, no surprise, I had to visit this place with my own car. I have to mention that I am not a professional photographer by any stretch of the imagination. I have a Nikon D7000 and a tripod, and tried to take some memorable photos during my visit.
